---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="CronixUI Developers" description="Developer docs for CronixUI">
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Developer docs</p>
    <h1>Build against the spec, not against one framework.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      CronixUI is designed so tokens, components, and exports stay aligned across every platform.
      The source of truth lives in `packages/spec/`.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel">
    <h2>Project layout</h2>
    <pre class="code">packages/
  spec/        design tokens + component schemas + generator
  web/         canonical CSS reference
  react/       React port
  vue/         Vue port
  svelte/      Svelte port
  solid/       Solid port
  flutter/     Flutter/Dart port
  python/      Python port
  go/          Go/Fyne port
  rust/        Rust/egui port</pre>
  </section>

  <section class="panel">
    <h2>Core commands</h2>
    <pre class="code">pnpm gen       # generate framework components from the spec
pnpm gen:all   # generate everything
pnpm build     # build all packages
pnpm docs:dev  # run docs locally
pnpm docs:build # build docs for deploy</pre>
  </section>

  <section class="panel">
    <h2>Adding a component</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Add the token or component definition to `packages/spec/`.</li>
      <li>Generate or update each framework implementation.</li>
      <li>Export the component from each package index.</li>
      <li>Document the component page in the docs site.</li>
      <li>Verify class names use the `cn-` prefix and tokens use `--cn-`.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="panel">
    <h2>Design rules</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Use `#0a0a0a` for background, `#f0ede8` for primary text, and `#6b2323` for accent.</li>
      <li>Prefer small, composable components with one clear responsibility.</li>
      <li>Keep component names and prop names consistent across frameworks.</li>
      <li>Favor accessibility: labels, keyboard support, and semantic markup.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="panel">
    <h2>Publishing</h2>
    <pre class="code">npm publish              # React, Svelte, Vue, Solid
cargo publish            # Rust
poetry publish           # Python
flutter pub publish      # Flutter
git tag v1.0.0 && git push --tags # Go versioning</pre>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
